Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.log

Class CategoryLog

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.log.AbstractTaskLog
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.log.CategoryLog
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<CategoryLog>
public class CategoryLog extends AbstractTaskLog implements Comparable<CategoryLog>
CategoryLog represents a log for tasks within a specific category. Extends AbstractTaskLog to inherit basic task log functionalities and implements Comparable to allow category logs to be compared by name.
Author:
Jayani Sivakumar, Diya Patel
